{"tid":207731,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血呢個節目既Like數同Share竟然一樣！算唔算網路奇蹟？","createTime":"2017-04-19T05:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T03:00:31.000Z","uid":30807,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfb8788de7811a9682c174641a45232a00758563","tid":207731,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/86/20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fprog%2F86%2F20&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=999e1ef8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/86/20</a><br />\n<br />\n2044 like<br />\n2044 share<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯一諗到既合理解釋就係每個有like既人都有share，已經諗唔到其他可能性<br />\n<br />\n見到親熱既網民咁團結齊心，我以後都係唔反熱了<br />\n<br />\n熱血<span style=\"color: red;\">製造</span>，最強頻道！"},{"pid":"a3c585a0173033cd77594033e4ed34492421e287","tid":207731,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L73MXKv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL73MXKv.png&h=db354200&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b868339037ba656a7356ac6d98066fe06884b097","tid":207731,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"我感動到想加入熱狗，有冇熱友可以話我知咩有咩途徑？"},{"pid":"1dcc74ac45b01c3563d2ca1e67edb7e7310991df","tid":207731,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:22:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1ed2e8ede9cd308f4b8a5eeab42cfe84fa63159","tid":207731,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb423ea4a166146082574ba60780ffd39271d8c4","tid":207731,"uid":30508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我不嬲都覺得 熱時係 用黎篤數 + 收不明來歷，唔見得光既錢，資金</blockquot