得光既錢，資金</blockquote><br />\n睇法一樣<br />\n熱時9成9文章都係網絡得黎而唔係採訪<br />\n真係廢到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n百9幾萬影左兩張相囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢踏實d慢慢做上去我覺得係有得做，但心急篤數呃廣告就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我已經多次係其他post質疑佢既在線人數，我就撚唔信深宵凌晨都有8千幾人在線睇佢地部機器畫畫<br />\n<br />\n試諗下，部機會跟你指示去畫野，如果真係咁多人，一人一句，跟本唔會畫到佢之前post出黎個d畫，只會係亂到九彩既一張圖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下chatroom 速度都知<br />\n佢地自稱live 有萬尻幾人睇 但係chatroom去得好慢<br />\n達哥 有6000幾人睇 而佢個chatroom係快到睇唔切 , 而達哥己經係開左 slow mode 每人30秒先可以發一次言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打呢個計法好有說服力，佢chatroom跟本就唔會旭"},{"pid":"eb9d4bc9353c3547e8a46ea76e824a19a278f05e","tid":207731,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"請問熱時最紅節目係邊個？大約有幾多人睇？"},{"pid":"18b164483336d3c7ca0f8e7dedf579c601f8c7f3","tid":207731,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb2c03e2c70a0f2db90c42de91ce57252ce934b8","tid":207731,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/pGOb8H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FpGOb8H.jpg&h=9f844dab&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係黃洋X真account???"},{"pid":"13f869ab13e2b8d5333e88c361b2c8fd19b61402","tid":207731,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/pGOb